        </p>
        <p class="AdvisoryBoardFull-content">
          After a plant-based diet changed his life, Pat shifted his focus to building and supporting businesses in the plant-based space.  He is the host of the popular Eat Green Make Green Podcast and is currently working on opening Boston's first fully plant-based cafe and beer garden.
